               <h2 class="box-title">Chopta Tungnath Chandrashila Trek is a popular trekking destination in Uttarakhand, India, offering a combination of natural beauty, spirituality,</h2>
               <p class="box-text mb-30">
                  <p>

</p>




<p>Chopta Tungnath &amp; Chandrashila Trek is the entire area comes under&nbsp;<a href="https://www.himalayanhikers.in/kedarnath-trek/">Kedarnath</a>&nbsp;musk deer sanctuary, District Rudraprayag Uttarakhand, Chopta at an approximate altitude of 2,608 m) so chances are that you can spot wildlife including wild goat and Himalayan monal in the morning.</p>               </p>
               <blockquote>
                  <p>  Most popularly known as the ‘Mini Switzerland’ of Uttarakhand, Himalayas</p>
               </blockquote>
               <div class="slider-area tour-slider1">
                  <div class="swiper th-slider mb-4" id="tourSlider4" data-slider-options='{"effect":"fade","loop":true,"thumbs":{"swiper":".tour-thumb-slider"},"autoplayDisableOnInteraction":"true"}'>
                     <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                        <div class="swiper-slide">
